WEBVTT

00:07.717 --> 00:10.504
[WOMAN SCREAMING]

00:11.929 --> 00:13.669
-Shut the fucking lid!
-Shut up.

00:13.890 --> 00:15.551
-I can't live like this.
-Shut up.

00:15.766 --> 00:18.553
