00:18.811 --> 00:21.143
[TARA GRUNTING]

00:21.606 --> 00:23.142
PAM:
Oh, my God.

00:28.321 --> 00:30.733
Don't ever try that again.

00:30.948 --> 00:34.486
Fuck you. You have no right.

00:35.870 --> 00:39.033
[MACHINE WHIRRING
AND TARA SCREAMING]

