02:34.864 --> 02:36.104
Bullshit!

02:36.324 --> 02:39.066
I can't keep lying.
We're gonna dig ourselves deeper.

02:39.285 --> 02:40.365
Think I enjoy it? Hm?

02:40.578 --> 02:43.991
I could have sold your peach-pie ass out
so many times, I done lost count.

02:44.206 --> 02:47.573
And the one motherfucking thing I needed
from you, Sook, is to zip it.

02:47.793 --> 02:50.125
-And this is how you do me?
-I didn't mention you.

02:50.338 --> 02:53.045
-No, you can save that for another day.
-Lafayette, please.

02:53.257 --> 02:55.339
We did so many terrible things.

02:55.551 --> 02:59.715
The only way to crawl out of this hole
is to start doing right.

03:00.222 --> 03:02.964
It's how Gran raised me.
Do the right thing, it'll be okay.

03:03.142 --> 03:04.882
Oh, yeah, baby. You survive.

03:05.102 --> 03:06.683
You always do.

03:06.896 --> 03:09.433
But, goddamn, do you leave a trail
of bodies behind.

03:09.648 --> 03:12.060
You know what?
You're the fucking angel of death.

03:20.117 --> 03:21.527
[SOBBING]

03:28.751 --> 03:30.992
MAN:
Don't fuck it up, gentlemen.

03:38.761 --> 03:42.128
Well, apart from these,
your escape ploy worked brilliantly.

03:42.348 --> 03:44.339
BILL:
I'm a bit surprised myself.

03:47.395 --> 03:50.637
We don't have many suspects
of who might have broken Russell out.

03:51.315 --> 03:53.180
Only four of us knew where he was.

03:59.698 --> 04:01.199
[CAR DOOR LOCK CHIRPING]

04:03.994 --> 04:05.404
|'|| drive.

04:12.586 --> 04:14.918
[NORA SCREAMING]

04:15.423 --> 04:16.754
NORA:
God!

04:18.843 --> 04:21.755
No, there is no one else!

04:23.389 --> 04:25.095
Nora?

04:25.516 --> 04:28.428
[NORA SCREAMING]

04:34.150 --> 04:36.436
She's holding out. I know it.

04:36.652 --> 04:38.517
She must have allies.

04:38.904 --> 04:40.644
Let's continue to torture her.

04:40.823 --> 04:42.654
Everyone breaks eventually.

04:42.867 --> 04:46.860
This cancer in our midst, how long
can we watch and wait before it kills us?

04:50.916 --> 04:52.076
No.

04:53.711 --> 04:55.167
I need you to talk to her.

04:55.713 --> 04:57.829
She loves you like a sister.

04:58.507 --> 05:02.125
You and only you can get her to open up,
give us the names.

05:03.929 --> 05:05.089
And if she doesn't?

05:06.140 --> 05:08.802
Then fuck it. We execute her publicly.

05:09.018 --> 05:13.057
Let the Sanguinistas know that we are
willing to kill just as much as they are.

05:14.064 --> 05:16.771
You know what could be persuasive? Hm?

05:16.942 --> 05:18.193
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

05:18.360 --> 05:21.397
Coming! I'm just--

05:21.614 --> 05:23.195
-What?
-What took you so long?

05:23.407 --> 05:24.943
I had the TV on. Whoa, whoa.

05:25.159 --> 05:26.695
lt's late, Sook. Can't this wait?

05:26.911 --> 05:29.573
Just-- Just be quiet for a second.
I'm turning myself in.

05:29.788 --> 05:31.289
-lnto what?
-lnto the police.

05:31.499 --> 05:32.614
I need you to arrest me.

05:32.833 --> 05:34.573
I killed Debbie Pelt!

05:34.793 --> 05:36.169
Are you listening to yourself?

05:36.378 --> 05:37.834
She came into my house with a shotgun.

05:38.047 --> 05:40.629
I turned it around on her,
blew her head clean off.

05:40.799 --> 05:43.131
I can take you to the body.
I'm not making this up.

05:43.344 --> 05:46.256
Shut up. Shut your mouth.
I don't wanna hear another word.

05:46.430 --> 05:51.220
I'm sick of it. I'm sick of lying
and covering and ruining people's lives.

05:51.435 --> 05:52.641
You gotta get out of here.

05:52.853 --> 05:55.640
