-I confessed to Alcide.

05:55.814 --> 05:59.306
He's gonna be at the station
in the morning. Just put me away.

05:59.527 --> 06:01.939
Ain't no way I'm gonna put you in jail.

06:04.782 --> 06:09.446
Just, uh-- Uh-- Act normal tomorrow, okay?
Don't do anything crazy.

06:09.662 --> 06:12.745
I'll try and find out how much
Andy knows...

06:13.707 --> 06:15.208
...and we'll think of something.

06:15.417 --> 06:17.578
-ls Alcide the only one who knows?
-No.

06:17.795 --> 06:19.501
Lafayette was there, and Tara.

06:19.713 --> 06:22.705
She took a bullet for me
and was more or less dead...

06:22.925 --> 06:26.008
...so we had Pam turn her to vampire.

06:26.845 --> 06:30.008
-You what?
-She was dying. I didn't have time to think.

06:30.808 --> 06:33.220
Jesus Christ!

06:34.770 --> 06:36.010
I told you.

06:36.230 --> 06:38.846
l ruin people's lives.

06:39.066 --> 06:41.273
Tara's a vampire.

06:43.571 --> 06:45.277
You gotta be fucking kidding me.

06:45.990 --> 06:47.605
Oh, good Lord.

06:47.825 --> 06:49.281
I'm gonna fucking kill her.

06:49.493 --> 06:53.702
Ginger, we're open till 4, bleach bucket!
Where is everyone?

06:53.914 --> 06:54.994
