I sent them all home.

06:55.165 --> 06:58.328
Oh, my God.
Sookie, you fucking did it.

07:01.630 --> 07:04.292
Well, no need for apologies, right?

07:04.466 --> 07:06.627
I'm certainly not waiting for one.

07:06.844 --> 07:09.381
