07:39.126 --> 07:40.332
Join me, will you?

07:49.386 --> 07:51.593
What's wrong? What's happened?

07:54.933 --> 07:57.094
BILL:
I remember the impulse.

07:57.311 --> 07:59.393
I had it myself for years.

08:00.439 --> 08:03.772
lt'll pass. I promise.

08:03.984 --> 08:06.316
Well, I can't ever do it again, even I wanted.

08:06.528 --> 08:09.520
