I command you," on me.

08:09.740 --> 08:13.073
Which is a card I'm surprised
y'all don't play more often.

08:17.081 --> 08:19.117
-Sookie know?
-What do you think?

08:20.000 --> 08:24.460
How many of us have nearly died
just to save her sorry ass?

08:25.005 --> 08:27.087
Well, I did them all one better.

08:29.718 --> 08:32.255
-ls Sookie safe?
-Don't.

08:32.471 --> 08:34.757
You can't keep asking yourself
that question.

08:34.973 --> 08:38.386
You can't worry about her
above everything else.

08:39.269 --> 08:40.349
Look where it got me.

08:41.522 --> 08:43.058
Gotta move on.

08:43.982 --> 08:45.483
Is she safe?

08:46.443 --> 08:47.603
Yeah.

08:48.987 --> 08:50.818
She's always safe.

08:50.989 --> 08:54.652
Because there'll always be some fool there
to take a bullet for her.

08:55.911 --> 08:57.572
Always.

08:59.790 --> 09:04.159
PAM: Aah!
-Stop fucking lying!

09:04.378 --> 09:07.040
I'm not lying. I swear.

09:07.256 --> 09:09.588
I don't know where Russell is.

09:14.805 --> 09:17.968
Look what's happened to you.

09:22.771 --> 09:24.602
A century together...

09:24.773 --> 09:28.812
...and never once have I ever done
anything to hurt you...

09:28.986 --> 09:30.476
...to hurt us.

09:30.654 --> 09:35.569
How could you think I would go
and dig up Russell Edgington?

09:36.493 --> 09:38.745
You're my maker, Eric...

09:38.912 --> 09:40.777
...and I would die for you, gladly...

09:40.956 --> 09:45.416
