before I would ever betray you.

09:45.627 --> 09:47.618
You know I would.

09:48.005 --> 09:50.121
And you'd be a fool.

09:50.716 --> 09:52.707
I trust no one.

09:52.926 --> 09:55.042
You shouldn't either.

09:57.431 --> 10:00.923
If I mean so little to you...

10:01.143 --> 10:02.974
...then why keep me around?

10:04.521 --> 10:09.231
If you can't trust me more than
Bill Compton or--

10:09.443 --> 10:11.934
Or a werewolf, for chrissake...

10:12.154 --> 10:14.520
...then release me and get it over with.

10:15.908 --> 10:19.196
Just say the words.

10:19.369 --> 10:23.954
"As your maker...

10:24.166 --> 10:26.373
...I release you."

10:27.377 --> 10:30.039
Say it and we're done.

10:32.925 --> 10:34.461
Say it!

11:02.704 --> 11:03.830
Not Pam.

11:04.039 --> 11:05.074
You're certain?

11:05.290 --> 11:06.871
She knows nothing.

11:09.044 --> 11:10.124
What did Tara say?

11:10.337 --> 11:13.625
Well, nothing to suggest that she or Pam
knew anything about Russell.

11:13.841 --> 11:16.924
There's no one else you've told?
Not even your sister?

11:17.094 --> 11:19.426
You mean the one who is in
the Authority?

11:21.181 --> 11:24.514
-l'd hope you think more of me.
-Russell's the martyr to the opposition.

11:24.726 --> 11:26.887
If she were planning a coup,
he could be useful.

11:27.104 --> 11:30.016
If Nora were planning a coup,
I would have known about it...

11:30.190 --> 11:34.274
...and I still wouldn't have given her Russell.
I'm not suicidal.

11:36.572 --> 11:39.405
Are you sure you didn't tell anyone?

11:39.575 --> 11:42.738
-Jessica?
-lf| had, we would have gone to her first.

11:43.787 --> 11:45.573
We need to go to ground.

11:46.540 --> 11:49.122
And tomorrow,
we'll have to cast the net wider.

11:50.669 --> 11:52.455
There's a leak somewhere.

11:54.798 --> 11:57.756
