17:55.617 --> 17:57.482
GORDON:
Go on.

17:59.246 --> 18:00.952
Mr. Pelt...

18:01.957 --> 18:03.663
...Mrs. Pelt...

18:05.418 --> 18:07.283
...l'm sorry to tell you...

18:08.421 --> 18:09.957
